Code:
```repl
import openpyxl
from openpyxl import load_workbook

# Load the workbook
wb_path = "/sandbox/input/input_spreadsheet/1_50088_init.xlsx"
wb = load_workbook(wb_path, data_only=False)  # keep formulas

# List sheet names
print("Sheet names:", wb.sheetnames)

for name in wb.sheetnames:
    ws = wb[name]
    print(f"\n--- Sheet: {name} ---")
    print("Max row:", ws.max_row, "Max column:", ws.max_column)

    # Get headers (first row)
    headers = [ws.cell(row=1, column=c).value for c in range(1, ws.max_column + 1)]
    print("Headers:", headers)

    # Print first 5 data rows (excluding header)
    print("First 5 data rows:")
    for r in range(2, min(ws.max_row, 6) + 1):
        row_vals = [ws.cell(row=r, column=c).value for c in range(1, ws.max_column + 1)]
        print(r, row_vals)

    # Print last 5 data rows
    start_last = max(2, ws.max_row - 4)
    print("Last 5 data rows:")
    for r in range(start_last, ws.max_row + 1):
        row_vals = [ws.cell(row=r, column=c).value for c in range(1, ws.max_column + 1)]
        print(r, row_vals)
```
2026-04-14 08:04:18,045 INFO RLM iteration 2/50
Reasoning: We inspected the workbook and found one sheet with columns A (header “A List”) and B (header “B List”). The task is to count how many times the letter “A” appears in column B, and additionally count “A” in column A when the corresponding cell in column B is empty. In the sample data this total is 3, which is already placed in cell F6 (row 6, column F) as a static number. We will replace that static value with a proper Excel formula that computes the count dynamically:

```
=COUNTIFS($B:$B,"A")+COUNTIFS($A:$A,"A",$B:$B,"")
```

This formula works in LibreOffice (COUNTIFS is supported) and returns the desired total. We will write it to cell F6, save the workbook to the output directory, run a recalculation, reload the file in data‑only mode, and verify that the computed value is present.
Code:
```repl
import openpyxl
from openpyxl import load_workbook
import os

# Paths
input_path = "/sandbox/input/input_spreadsheet/1_50088_init.xlsx"
output_dir = "/sandbox/output/output_spreadsheet/"
os.makedirs(output_dir, exist_ok=True)
output_path = os.path.join(output_dir, "1_50088_init.xlsx")

# Load workbook (keep formulas)
wb = load_workbook(input_path, data_only=False)
ws = wb.active  # only one sheet

# Write formula into the target cell (F6)
formula = '=COUNTIFS($B:$B,"A")+COUNTIFS($A:$A,"A",$B:$B,"")'
ws["F6"] = formula

# Save to output location
wb.save(output_path)

# Recalculate formulas
recalc_result = await recalculate(output_path)
print("Recalculate result:", recalc_result)

# Reload with data_only to read the computed value
wb2 = load_workbook(output_path, data_only=True)
ws2 = wb2.active
computed = ws2["F6"].value
print("Computed value in F6 after recalculation:", computed)
```
